data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of Arvin, California! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is perfectly situated in a peaceful cul-de-sac, offering both tranquility and convenience. With its spacious interior, bonus sun-room, and prime location within walking distance of Kovacevich Park and Arvin High School, this property is a rare find. The home features a large master bedroom, offering a private sanctuary to unwind after a long day. The kitchen is adorned with elegant granite countertops, making meal preparation a pleasure. It's the perfect space for culinary enthusiasts. Contact your favorite agent today to schedule your very own private showing!
